seo: Apache Axis2,HappyAxis.jsp,信息泄露漏洞,检测
summary: 检测Apache Axis2是否存在HappyAxis.jsp页面导致的信息泄露漏洞，攻击者可能利用此漏洞获取敏感信息进行进一步攻击。
summary_en: Detect whether there is an information disclosure vulnerability caused by the HappyAxis.jsp page in Apache Axis2. Attackers may exploit this vulnerability to obtain sensitive information for further attacks.
